					"value": "While the player is walking over a banter spot in LOW, they experience a sudden shiver and a shock, physically feeling Haarlep connecting to their body to turn into it. They realise they are going to have to endure knowing that Haarlep is using their image for sex somewhere in Hell forever.\r\n\r\nIf Astarion is present, he will show some sympathy, or draw comparisons to his own experience.\r\n"
